  "root_text": {
    "snp5.2:0.1": "Sutta Nipāta 5.2 ",
    "snp5.2:0.2": "Ajitamāṇavapucchā ",
    "snp5.2:1.1": "“Kenassu nivuto loko, ",
    "snp5.2:1.2": "(iccāyasmā ajito) ",
    "snp5.2:1.3": "Kenassu nappakāsati; ",
    "snp5.2:1.4": "Kissābhilepanaṁ brūsi, ",
    "snp5.2:1.5": "Kiṁsu tassa mahabbhayaṁ”. ",
    "snp5.2:2.1": "“Avijjāya nivuto loko, ",
    "snp5.2:2.2": "(ajitāti bhagavā) ",
    "snp5.2:2.3": "Vevicchā pamādā nappakāsati; ",
    "snp5.2:2.4": "Jappābhilepanaṁ brūmi, ",
    "snp5.2:2.5": "Dukkhamassa mahabbhayaṁ”. ",
    "snp5.2:3.1": "“Savanti sabbadhi sotā, ",
    "snp5.2:3.2": "(iccāyasmā ajito) ",
    "snp5.2:3.3": "Sotānaṁ kiṁ nivāraṇaṁ; ",
    "snp5.2:3.4": "Sotānaṁ saṁvaraṁ brūhi, ",
    "snp5.2:3.5": "Kena sotā pidhiyyare”. ",
    "snp5.2:4.1": "“Yāni sotāni lokasmiṁ, ",
    "snp5.2:4.2": "(ajitāti bhagavā) ",
    "snp5.2:4.3": "Sati tesaṁ nivāraṇaṁ; ",
    "snp5.2:4.4": "Sotānaṁ saṁvaraṁ brūmi, ",
    "snp5.2:4.5": "Paññāyete pidhiyyare”. ",
    "snp5.2:5.1": "“Paññā ceva sati yañca, ",
    "snp5.2:5.2": "(iccāyasmā ajito) ",
    "snp5.2:5.3": "Nāmarūpañca mārisa; ",
    "snp5.2:5.4": "Etaṁ me puṭṭho pabrūhi, ",
    "snp5.2:5.5": "Katthetaṁ uparujjhati”. ",
    "snp5.2:6.1": "“Yametaṁ pañhaṁ apucchi, ",
    "snp5.2:6.2": "ajita taṁ vadāmi te; ",
    "snp5.2:6.3": "Yattha nāmañca rūpañca, ",
    "snp5.2:6.4": "asesaṁ uparujjhati; ",
    "snp5.2:6.5": "Viññāṇassa nirodhena, ",
    "snp5.2:6.6": "etthetaṁ uparujjhati”. ",
    "snp5.2:7.1": "“Ye ca saṅkhātadhammāse, ",
    "snp5.2:7.2": "ye ca sekhā puthū idha; ",
    "snp5.2:7.3": "Tesaṁ me nipako iriyaṁ, ",
    "snp5.2:7.4": "puṭṭho pabrūhi mārisa”. ",
    "snp5.2:8.1": "“Kāmesu nābhigijjheyya, ",
    "snp5.2:8.2": "Manasānāvilo siyā; ",
    "snp5.2:8.3": "Kusalo sabbadhammānaṁ, ",
    "snp5.2:8.4": "Sato bhikkhu paribbaje”ti. ",
    "snp5.2:8.5": "Ajitamāṇavapucchā paṭhamā. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "snp5.2:0.1": "Anthology of Discourses 5.2 ",
    "snp5.2:0.2": "The Questions of Ajita ",
    "snp5.2:1.1": "“By what is the world shrouded?” ",
    "snp5.2:1.2": "said Venerable Ajita. ",
    "snp5.2:1.3": "“Why does it not shine? ",
    "snp5.2:1.4": "Tell me, what is its tar pit? ",
    "snp5.2:1.5": "What is its greatest fear?” ",
    "snp5.2:2.1": "“The world is shrouded in ignorance.” ",
    "snp5.2:2.2": "replied the Buddha. ",
    "snp5.2:2.3": "“Avarice and negligence make it not shine. ",
    "snp5.2:2.4": "Muttered prayer is its tar pit. ",
    "snp5.2:2.5": "Suffering is its greatest fear.” ",
    "snp5.2:3.1": "“The streams flow everywhere,” ",
    "snp5.2:3.2": "said Venerable Ajita. ",
    "snp5.2:3.3": "“What is there to block them? ",
    "snp5.2:3.4": "And tell me the restraint of streams—",
    "snp5.2:3.5": "by what are they locked out?” ",
    "snp5.2:4.1": "“The streams in the world,” ",
    "snp5.2:4.2": "replied the Buddha, ",
    "snp5.2:4.3": "“are blocked by mindfulness. ",
    "snp5.2:4.4": "I tell you the restraint of streams—",
    "snp5.2:4.5": "they are locked out by wisdom.” ",
    "snp5.2:5.1": "“That wisdom and mindfulness,” ",
    "snp5.2:5.2": "said Venerable Ajita, ",
    "snp5.2:5.3": "“and that which is name and form, good fellow; ",
    "snp5.2:5.4": "when questioned, please tell me of this: ",
    "snp5.2:5.5": "where does this all cease?” ",
    "snp5.2:6.1": "“This question which you have asked, ",
    "snp5.2:6.2": "I shall answer you, Ajita. ",
    "snp5.2:6.3": "Where name and form ",
    "snp5.2:6.4": "cease with nothing left over—",
    "snp5.2:6.5": "with the cessation of consciousness, ",
    "snp5.2:6.6": "here they cease.” ",
    "snp5.2:7.1": "“There are those who have appraised the teaching, ",
    "snp5.2:7.2": "and many kinds of trainees here. ",
    "snp5.2:7.3": "Now you, being alert, are asked ",
    "snp5.2:7.4": "to tell me their behavior, good fellow.’ ",
    "snp5.2:8.1": "“Not greedy for sensual pleasures, ",
    "snp5.2:8.2": "their mind would be unclouded. ",
    "snp5.2:8.3": "Skilled in all things, ",
    "snp5.2:8.4": "a mendicant would wander mindful.” "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "snp5.2:3.5": "pidhiyyare → pithīyare (bj-a); pithiyyare (sya-all, pts-vp-pli1); pidhīyare (?) ",
